    "As shown in Figure 1, we adapt the mixer W to fuse all the possible subspaces (i.e., A i B j).",
    "Compared to LoRA, MoSLoRA requires negligible extra parameters since d 1 + d 2 ≫ r. Similarly to LoRA, MoSLoRA can also be merged into the original weights, and thus introduce no latency during inference.",
    "We perform experiments on various downstream tasks, including commonsense reasoning tasks finetuning LLaMA 3 (AI@Meta, 2024), visual instruction tuning on LLaVA-1.5 (Liu et al., 2023a) series models, and subject-driven text-to-image generation on Stable Diffusion XL (SDXL) model (Podell et al., 2023).",
